data.meta_description: Henry Washington Younger was born in the year 1810, son of Charles Lee Younger and Sarah Sullivan Purcell. He was married  to Bersheba Leighton Fristoe, they had 3 children. He died in the year 1862. This information is part of Genealogy Richard Remmé, The Hague, Netherlands by Richard Remmé on Genealogy Online.
